date.\\n\\nConcrete evidence:\\n- The Gradle native test fails in `TypeUtilTest.convertsValuesWithRegisteredValueOfMethods()` after entering `TypeUtil.valueOf(...)`; the native run reports `java.lang.NoSuchMethodException: java.lang.Boolean.valueOf(java.lang.String)` and the assertion then fails.\\n- The native trace verify loop repeatedly stops on missing reflection for boxed primitive `valueOf(String)` methods: `Byte` in cycle 1, `Double` in cycle 2, `Float` in cycle 3, `Integer` in cycle 4, `Long` in cycle 5, `Short` in cycle 6, then `Boolean.valueOf(String)` invocation in cycles 7 and 8.\\n- The committed metadata file remains `{}`, so the run never converged to a usable metadata patch.\\n\\nPlease inspect:\\n- `logs/org.mortbay.jetty:jetty-util:6.1.26/native-test-verify/cycle-7-runNativeTraceImage-2026-05-03T17-14-47-603510Z.log`\\n- `logs/org.mortbay.jetty:jetty-util:6.1.26/native-test-verify/cycle-8-runNativeTraceImage-2026-05-03T17-15-27-056826Z.log`\\n- `logs/org.mortbay.jetty:jetty-util:6.1.26/native-test-verify/cycle-1-runNativeTraceImage-2026-05-03T17-11-14-449025Z.log` through `cycle-6-runNativeTraceImage-2026-05-03T17-14-07-429211Z.log`\\n\\nManual next steps:\\n1. Recover or rewrite the `TypeUtil`-specific test so it is persisted under `tests/src/org.mortbay.jetty/jetty-util/6.1.26/...` instead of leaving the scaffold placeholder.\\n2. Add the missing reflection metadata for the boxed primitive `valueOf(String)` methods exercised by `TypeUtil.valueOf(...)`, then rerun native trace/native test for this coordinate.\\n3. Expand coverage beyond the current `TypeUtil` path or refresh the generated tests so dynamic-access coverage clears the 50% gate.\"}}\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
